Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:56.85,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all the way to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tom-san told me one of his family members\Nat home is also a shipwright, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must've been difficult to come to Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trained by Tom-san since I was a kid and I came here with a ship that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you were my brother's pupil,\NI bet it's quite a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's called the Thousand Sunny\Nand it's my masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after we entered Fishman Island,\Nit was taken away by the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of reason that I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could give me a clue\Nas to the Sunny's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When a ship sinks in these parts, it usually gets carried by the tide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and ends up at a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Sunny will be there too.\NDon not worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get there soon.\NThe place known as the Sea Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait, Megalo!\NWhere are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-sama, Brother-sama,\Neverybody at the palace, please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going out without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be home by dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for a "walk"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on, Megalo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he left the doors open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What if something happens to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeleton, hurry up!\NSee if the Princess is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're riding my bones too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here!\NPrincess Shirahoshi is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The Mermaid Princess is not here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! This is a matter\Nof great consequence to the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this happen?! Who did this?!\NShe must have been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She must've been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate that connects\NFishman Island and Ryugu Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the switch to open it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeleton, hurry and go back to Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to tell him what is going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to do as we're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us the only way we'll live\Nis if we obey them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are "they"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kill us if you don't tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about!
