Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are such lowly creatures—\Nthey can't even breathe in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you pirates under the control of Hody Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all be happy!\NBecause you can be part of this historic mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Vander Decken of the Flying Dutchman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain of that cursed ghost ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm his descendant. I'm not a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I am cursed as well.\NI can't swim even though I'm a Fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this devil power\Nalongside the Mark-Mark curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you human right there! Step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys serious?\NDon't be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hachi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.83,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hatchan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hachi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hatchan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Energy Steroids will do nothing but ruin you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of destroying this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Great Knight Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi-san, give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear your voice anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you were an officer of the pirate group I admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You became a coward.\NIt's time for a generation change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To teach the humans a lesson,\Nwe need Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So Neptune is in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You all taught us that we're the supreme race!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But Arlong-san lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Decken! Hyouzou!\NWhy are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You even refused Arlong-san's offer back then
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so why are you helping these youths now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping? I'm just in this for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong was stingy so he couldn't pay me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt sorry for him that he could only take crappy swordsmen like you with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi from the Arlong Pirates?\NOh, sweet memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your captain even tried to make me\Nwork under him back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was ridiculous!\NI won't work under anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody understands that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong-san had a dream\Nand an ability to take action that I could respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the same time,\Nhe was too rough and lacked cleverness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you guys were running wild on the sea, we were all too young to become pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We all witnessed what they did so we plan things more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we've learned\Nfrom our predecessors' failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will continue where Arlong left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As a member of the group I admired so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your opposition is so discouraging, Hachi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy who shattered Arlong's dream is here, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't mind at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He called me his friend even though\NI'm a former member of the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of you are my friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, Straw Hat Luffy saved my life. I wish I could go see him now but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too ashamed to face him when somebody is trying to keep Arlong's dream alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic of you\Nto become friends with a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disgusted by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm locked on to you, Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgot how pirates do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is something to say, you have to use violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he throwing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I touched you just now,\Nyou became my mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I throw\Nor where I throw it, it's like a living bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it will strike you at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The knife he just threw somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Flew at the octopus Fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mark-Mark curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there are a number of ways\Nto defend yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No... You have so many arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew about your power—I heard the rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hody, he's trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As he told you, Hachi-san.\NVander Decken is not working under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We are allies on equal footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're annoying me anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!\NRun, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But they will chase you, chase you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,chase you and chase you to the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, now I can get away!\NIn the water, the arrows will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! They aren't even slowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have two marks—one for each palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't washed my right hand for ten years
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since I touched Princess Shirahoshi and designated her as my mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? It doesn't matter if it's love or a weapon that I throw,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll both follow until the furthest reaches of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he could continue stalking her insidiously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,without showing himself\Nor getting caught by Neptune's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sinister guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinister! Sinister! Sinister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sinister! Sinister! Sinister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you human pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen Decken's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the first stage of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the Ryugu Palace is impregnable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,someone has been able to pierce the defenses for ten years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's him—Vander Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So for this mission, you'll be thrown by Decken
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and fly to the Mermaid Princess in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you'll be landing\Nis the solid wall of the tower though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, open the gate from inside the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and let us in—that is your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! If we get thrown...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We could die from hitting the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want you humans to do it because your lives aren't that important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You humans are less valuable than slaves here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who survive\Nhitting the wall carry out your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you succeed, I'll set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse to do it,\NI'll kick you out of the bubble right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You lowly creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...\NIf we leave the bubble, we'll drown for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you have no choice\Nbut wager on the possibility you'll survive, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, a new history for the Fishmen will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we conquer the Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to you soon, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:13.72,Sign,,0,0,265,,{\fad(496,496)\blur0.6\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(451,496,\1a&H00&)\t(4014,4059,\1a&HFF&)}Ryugu Palace, Northwest Side\NPassageway to the Hard Shell Tower
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.21,0:17:13.72,Sign,,0,0,265,,{\fad(496,496)\bord0\blur0.6\4a&HFF&}Ryugu Palace, Northwest Side\NPassageway to the Hard Shell Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.68,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.05,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Skeleton,\Nget to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... We have to open the gate or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody will kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I have a question for you guys. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, you have to stay in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, at that place\Ncalled Ryugu Palace... Is she there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She is there!\NSo what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go.\NEven if it kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going?! You never learn! If she's beautiful, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she's beautiful, isn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met her\Nbut I heard she's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's beautiful,\Njust as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go, I'll go, at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now lead me to Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know but we have to take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be handcuffed if you're going to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want\Nas long as I can see the Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cook for the Mermaid Princess\Nif you handcuff me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were gonna resist!\NCart them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards wanna ruin my chance to get close to the Mermaid Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?! Do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you beat all the soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't do anything wrong but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their fault—they tried to handcuff me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're part of the Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Such dangerous people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everybody's looking at us coldly like they're a bunch of deep-sea fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining!\NWhat's done is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Think before you act!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You beat the half of them with kung fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were pretty strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to compliment me, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the voice of a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a man covered with blood at the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guy from the Fishman District!\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Call a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I am a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hachi!\NIt's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you hurt?!\NWhat happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... It's you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you...\NIs Straw Hat with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here! Wait for a moment!\NI'll treat you in a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon all your friends... Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't wanna get involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with this island!\NGet off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Fishman Pirates will come\Nand attack the island soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ryugu Kingdom will... fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a kidnapping! Somebody kidnapped the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And pirates are falling like rain\Nat the tower! In any event,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they're your enemies!\NThey're attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapped?! Shirahoshi?! Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy attack, now?\NWhat should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now?!\NWe're occupying the palace ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Don't answer"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for us to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to open the gate at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come out of Shark now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'd rather stay in here still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like it out here after ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is racing!\NThis is very bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it be bad?\NYou just got out of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what they call an adventure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If your heart is racing,\Nthat's an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "the Sea Forest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?\NSomething fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a grave\Nthat I haven't been to since they built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the place I've wanted to go to the most\Nfor the past ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:46.45,Sign,,0,0,265,,{\fad(441,441)\blur0.6\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(396,441,\1a&H00&)\t(4459,4504,\1a&HFF&)}Sea Forest in the deep sea
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.54,0:22:46.45,Sign,,0,0,265,,{\fad(441,441)\bord0\blur0.6\4a&HFF&}Sea Forest in the deep sea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:48.18,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,It's been ten years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since her assassination in broad daylight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that threw Fishman Island into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How time flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The princes have grown into tough soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi is still in the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody forgets your ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody's plans for revenge are underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirates he has sent\Nlay siege to Ryugu Palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and throw it into a state of panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew has been caught up in the attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the once impregnable Ryugu Palace gate is breached.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Fishman Pirates have arrived—\Nintent on destroying the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hody's Onslaught\NThe Retaliatory Plan Set Into Motion"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
